summary: A sweet shack for a cool stay
descriptionHtml:
A small sweet shack for a cool stay. Some sweet treats to eat and a new weapon for you.  All just for fun, probably not lore friendly. It is a shack so sometimes the weather comes inside. There is a bed, alchemy and enchanting stations and a tanning rack. Sit out on the deck and listen to the windchimes. Hope you enjoy this sweet retreat.

 Added a short video and pics.
